Heritage is a kinetic &ldquo;precision frame&rdquo; (slug) shotgun that can drop from the 2nd and 3rd encounters of the Deep Stone Crypt raid. After the initial drop, you have a chance of getting additional rolls from the raid&rsquo;s secret chests.
PvP Thoughts Heritage has the highest aim assist of any slug shotgun. Drewsky says &ldquo;this weapon is really comparable to The Chaperone.&rdquo;
The base one hit kill range is 10.5m, you can increase that up to 11.
